cz.zcu.kiv.multicloud.utils

Class SecureFileCredentialStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.zcu.kiv.multicloud.utils.FileCredentialStore
      • cz.zcu.kiv.multicloud.utils.SecureFileCredentialStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CredentialStore

    public class SecureFileCredentialStore
extends FileCredentialStore
implements CredentialStore
    cz.zcu.kiv.multicloud.utils/SecureFileCredentialStore.java

    Implementation of the CredentialStore using simple {java.io.File} as a base for storing the tokens. This implementation uses AES file encryption for improving security of stored tokens. Use of default password is not advised.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jaromír Staněk
